    <summary>Smassh your Keyboard, TUI Edition</summary>
    <description># Smassh

Smassh is a TUI based typing test application inspired by MonkeyType — a popular online web-based typing application.

Smassh tries to be a full-fledged typing test experience without missing out on looks and feel.

**Note:** Smassh uses [Nerd Fonts](https://www.nerdfonts.com/) for icons by default. If a Nerd Font is not installed, icons may display incorrectly.

# Screenshots

![Screenshot 1](https://cdn.statically.io/gh/Aurocosh/chocolatey-packages/master/automatic/smassh/img/screenshot1.png)

![Screenshot 2](https://cdn.statically.io/gh/Aurocosh/chocolatey-packages/master/automatic/smassh/img/screenshot2.png)

![Screenshot 3](https://cdn.statically.io/gh/Aurocosh/chocolatey-packages/master/automatic/smassh/img/screenshot3.png)

![Screenshot 4](https://cdn.statically.io/gh/Aurocosh/chocolatey-packages/master/automatic/smassh/img/screenshot4.png)

# Features

- Interactive and beautiful UI
- Words and time modes for typing
- Real-time comparison of speed carets
- Change styles and settings on the fly
- Multiple theme support
- Multiple language support
- Lots of options to tweak

# Tweaks

| Tweak | Description |
| ----- | ----------- |
| Blind mode | You would not be able to see your mistakes |
| Capital Letters | Some letters in your tasks will be capitalized |
| Caret Style | Caret style matters |
| Confidence mode | Try typing without backspace |
| Cursor Buddy | Set up your cursor buddy to run along with you |
| Difficulty | Choose how strict smassh should be with wrong keypresses |
| Force Correct | You cannot continue without clearing mistakes |
| Min Accuracy | Fall below this average accuracy and you fail |
| Min Burst | Fall below this average burst for even a word and you fail |
| Min Speed | Fall below this average speed and you fail |
| Tab Reset | Reset the test quickly with Tab |

</description>
